540
00:21:20,781 --> 00:21:22,282
Learning about
your beloved humanity.

541
00:21:22,491 --> 00:21:23,951
By dancing at my club?

542
00:21:24,159 --> 00:21:25,077
Well, I saw all the people

543
00:21:25,285 --> 00:21:27,120
