and I wanted to discover

544
00:21:27,329 --> 00:21:28,914
what they were so happy about.

545
00:21:29,122 --> 00:21:31,833
Oh, is it possible it's
the money that I pay them?

546
00:21:32,042 --> 00:21:33,168
It's possible.

547
00:21:34,044 --> 00:21:36,546
But I have to admit
that when I started dancing,

548
00:21:36,755 --> 00:21:38,715
rubbing up against
the other humans,

549
00:21:39,633 --> 00:21:40,968
I got a tingling
sensation...

550
