pleased by my effort.

554
00:21:47,641 --> 00:21:49,434
Disturbed is more like it.

555
00:21:50,352 --> 00:21:52,312
Are you actually trying
to systematically disrupt

556
00:21:52,521 --> 00:21:54,189
- every part of my life?
- No.

557
