I'm trying to <i>learn</i> about
every part of your life.

558
00:21:57,317 --> 00:21:57,985
Oh, right.

559
00:21:58,193 --> 00:21:59,444
How's that going for you so far?

560
00:21:59,653 --> 00:22:01,613
Well, quite
illuminating, actually.

561
00:22:02,155 --> 00:22:05,033
I understand now why you
have this provocative club.

562
00:22:05,242 --> 00:22:07,327
I understand why
you amused yourself

563
00:22:07,536 --> 00:22:09,329
- with that
curvaceous savage.
- (sighs)

564
00:22:09,538 --> 00:22:10,956
But what I don't
understand...

565
00:22:11,164 --> 00:22:12,416
Is my human job. Yes, I know.

566
00:22:12,624 --> 00:22:15,669
It's very simple:
I'm a civilian consultant.

567
00:22:16,211 --> 00:22:18,338
But why do you
still punish people?

568
00:22:19,172 --> 00:22:20,257
It's what I've always done.

569
