That's not true.

570
00:22:21,675 --> 00:22:23,844
That's who your father
wanted you to be.

571
00:22:25,637 --> 00:22:28,015
Are you still trying
to win him over?

572
00:22:28,557 --> 00:22:29,558
Careful, Mother.

573
00:22:30,183 --> 00:22:31,143
Why?

574
00:22:31,351 --> 00:22:32,728
Are you going
to punish me?

575
00:22:49,578 --> 00:22:50,829
LEILA:
I'm sorry, Detective.

576
00:22:51,246 --> 00:22:52,956
I looked into
the two videos in question,

577
00:22:53,165 --> 00:22:54,958
and unfortunately,
there was no overlap.

578
00:22:55,375 --> 00:22:56,376
CHLOE:
Doesn't make any sense.

579
00:22:56,710 --> 00:22:58,462
I'll need a list of everyone
who saw the videos.

580
00:22:58,879 --> 00:23:01,715
Sadly, we don't track people,
just I.P. addresses.

581
00:23:01,923 --> 00:23:04,926
(sighs) Maybe I'm looking
at this the wrong way.

582
00:23:05,844 --> 00:23:07,846
Can you take me through how
your video process works?

583
00:23:08,055 --> 00:23:10,390
Well, our users can upload
anything they want.

584
00:23:10,599 --> 00:23:12,392
And if we find that
the content's inappropriate--

585
00:23:12,976 --> 00:23:15,687
uh, anything from
animal cruelty to beheadings--

586
00:23:15,896 --> 00:23:17,064
it gets taken down.

587
00:23:17,397 --> 00:23:18,398
By who?

588
00:23:18,899 --> 00:23:20,233
Our content moderators.

589
00:23:20,650 --> 00:23:21,276
Huh.

590
00:23:21,485 --> 00:23:23,195
LEILA: Most of them
only last a few months.

591
00:23:23,487 --> 00:23:24,237
Frankly, most people

592
00:23:24,446 --> 00:23:26,448
can't stomach something
so dark or upsetting.

593
00:23:26,907 --> 00:23:29,576
- Right.
- (Lucifer laughing)

594
00:23:29,785 --> 00:23:31,203
LUCIFER:
God, that has got to smart.

595
00:23:31,411 --> 00:23:32,287
(Lucifer laughs)

596
00:23:32,496 --> 00:23:34,247
Can I see that again?

597
00:23:36,041 --> 00:23:36,666
Lucifer?

598
00:23:37,292 --> 00:23:38,585
Oh, Detective.
You're here.

599
00:23:38,835 --> 00:23:40,170
Did you know that this room

600
00:23:40,379 --> 00:23:42,005
collects all the best parts
of the Internet?

601
00:23:42,297 --> 00:23:43,715
- Can I talk to you for a second?
- Yeah, yeah.

602
00:23:43,924 --> 00:23:45,675
But you got to see this--
a-a naked man

603
00:23:45,884 --> 00:23:47,469
thinks he can jump
on the back of a rhino.

604
00:23:47,677 --> 00:23:49,930
(laughs): You'll never
guess what he lands on.

605
00:23:50,138 --> 00:23:51,431
Actually, you probably will.

606
00:23:52,474 --> 00:23:53,809
What? You've seen it already?

607
00:23:56,228 --> 00:23:57,145
(sighs)

608
00:23:58,355 --> 00:23:59,189
What are you doing here?

609
00:23:59,564 --> 00:24:00,857
Trying to catch our killer.

610
00:24:01,066 --> 00:24:02,442
- Duh.
- I thought you didn't care

611
00:24:02,651 --> 00:24:04,986
- whether this sicko
was brought to justice.
- Oh, I don't.

612
00:24:05,195 --> 00:24:07,155
But then I realized that
our killer may have the answer

613
00:24:07,364 --> 00:24:09,449
to a question that I'm,
you know, struggling with.

614
00:24:09,866 --> 00:24:10,492
Mm.

615
00:24:11,076 --> 00:24:12,035
Why does he punish?

616
00:24:12,786 --> 00:24:13,495
That's it?

617
00:24:13,954 --> 00:24:15,956
First you want to teach
this vigilante a lesson,

618
00:24:16,164 --> 00:24:17,874
- and now you want to
have a talk with him?
- Yes.

619
00:24:18,083 --> 00:24:19,543
And lucky for me, I found out
where you were headed.

620
00:24:19,751 --> 00:24:22,170
(chuckles): I mean,
these videos are enthralling.

621
00:24:22,379 --> 00:24:24,047
CHLOE: No, I-I can't.
I can't watch these.

622
00:24:24,256 --> 00:24:25,549
- (growling)
- LUCIFER:
Oh, I've seen worse.

623
00:24:25,757 --> 00:24:27,968
But never so many collected
in one single room.

624
00:24:28,176 --> 00:24:29,302
You know, if I ever
go back to Hell,

625
00:24:29,511 --> 00:24:31,138
I am getting me
one of these.

626
00:24:31,930 --> 00:24:33,598
Selfish bastards
get to see everything.

627
00:24:33,807 --> 00:24:36,518
(woman screaming over video)

628
00:24:36,726 --> 00:24:38,562
- (scoffs)
- Yeah.

629
00:24:40,355 --> 00:24:41,273
They do.

630
00:24:41,982 --> 00:24:43,275
I know where
the overlap is.

631
00:24:47,988 --> 00:24:49,865
♪♪

632
00:25:16,516 --> 00:25:17,476
(sighs)

633
00:25:19,144 --> 00:25:20,187
(knock on door)

634
00:25:21,605 --> 00:25:23,607
MAZE: Amenadiel,
I know you're in there.

635
00:25:25,984 --> 00:25:27,068
(vacuum whirring)

636
00:25:27,277 --> 00:25:28,236
Open up!

637
00:25:31,656 --> 00:25:32,782
(vacuum stops)

638
00:25:34,659 --> 00:25:35,619
Hey.

639
00:25:40,373 --> 00:25:42,209
What are you hiding?

640
00:25:43,793 --> 00:25:44,419
Nothing.

641
00:25:44,628 --> 00:25:45,378
(chuckles)

642
00:25:49,633 --> 00:25:51,051
(laughs):
Oh.

643
00:25:54,513 --> 00:25:56,097
I see what's going on with you.

644
00:25:58,308 --> 00:25:59,935
- You do?
- Sure.

645
00:26:00,143 --> 00:26:02,812
Humans say that rebound sex
is important after a breakup.

646
00:26:03,605 --> 00:26:05,690
You don't have to hide
that you're getting some.

647
00:26:06,358 --> 00:26:07,234
(laughs)

648
00:26:07,651 --> 00:26:08,652
I'm not.

649
00:26:11,530 --> 00:26:12,280
Right.

650
00:26:13,698 --> 00:26:15,450
Of course. I didn't want you
to feel awkward.

651
00:26:16,243 --> 00:26:17,244
Silly me.

652
00:26:20,288 --> 00:26:21,456
(sighs)

653
00:26:23,124 --> 00:26:24,042
So what are
you doing here?

654
00:26:26,169 --> 00:26:27,546
I have a problem.

655
00:26:28,171 --> 00:26:29,089
I need your help.

656
00:26:30,215 --> 00:26:31,508
There's a new...

657
00:26:31,925 --> 00:26:34,052
woman in Lucifer's life.

658
00:26:34,511 --> 00:26:37,472
