from both of us.

661
00:26:40,976 --> 00:26:41,768
I am.

662
00:26:44,271 --> 00:26:46,398
- But before I do,
I need you...
- I'll talk to him.

663
00:26:46,731 --> 00:26:47,482
Yeah.

664
00:26:52,028 --> 00:26:52,904
Well, that was easy.

665
00:26:53,655 --> 00:26:54,614
I'm his big brother, Maze.

666
00:26:54,823 --> 00:26:56,825
I really should start looking
out for him more often.

667
00:26:58,994 --> 00:26:59,911
Okay.

668
00:27:01,830 --> 00:27:02,706
Thank you.

669
00:27:04,916 --> 00:27:06,001
All right. Thanks.

670
00:27:06,293 --> 00:27:07,961
Dan's working with
Wobble to trace

671
00:27:08,169 --> 00:27:09,754
what moderator may have
pulled both videos.

672
00:27:09,963 --> 00:27:11,006
Hopefully, we'll
have an answer soon.

673
00:27:11,214 --> 00:27:12,215
Then why are you
so sure the killer's

674
00:27:12,424 --> 00:27:13,675
one of these misanthropes?

675
00:27:14,134 --> 00:27:15,051
CHLOE:
Well, serial killers

676
00:27:15,260 --> 00:27:16,469
usually start with
someone they know.

677
00:27:16,678 --> 00:27:18,221
If the killer worked
here, they knew Nick,

678
00:27:18,430 --> 00:27:20,015
saw how much the
prank hurt Tommy.

679
00:27:20,223 --> 00:27:21,850
So you think
seeing someone they recognized

680
00:27:22,058 --> 00:27:24,644
in one of these twisted videos
finally made them snap?

681
00:27:25,145 --> 00:27:26,813
Maybe it awakened
something in them.

682
00:27:27,689 --> 00:27:30,233
Something that was always there,
just fighting to get out.

683
00:27:30,817 --> 00:27:32,235
(chuckles) But...

684
00:27:33,695 --> 00:27:35,572
they were just
trying to do a job.

685
00:27:36,740 --> 00:27:37,866
Job no one else wanted.

686
00:27:38,241 --> 00:27:39,659
Well, maybe they chose
that for a reason.

687
00:27:39,868 --> 00:27:42,829
No one chooses
to be a sin-eater, Detective.

688
00:27:44,748 --> 00:27:46,291
No one wants
to be custodian

689
00:27:46,499 --> 00:27:48,168
of the world's filth.
Why would they?

690
00:27:48,585 --> 00:27:51,796
Absorbing the worst humanity has
to offer, day in and day out.

691
00:27:52,964 --> 00:27:53,840
Changes you.

692
00:27:54,299 --> 00:27:55,425
So you think
it's the job's fault

693
00:27:55,634 --> 00:27:56,593
that they started to punish?

694
00:27:56,801 --> 00:27:58,261
People don't
arrive broken.

695
00:27:59,137 --> 00:28:00,805
They start with passion
and yearning

696
00:28:01,556 --> 00:28:04,434
till something comes along that
disabuses them of those notions.

697
00:28:05,310 --> 00:28:06,186
Hmm.

698
00:28:08,104 --> 00:28:10,940
Which means... that none
of these people did it.

699
00:28:11,149 --> 00:28:12,233
Okay. I'm not following.

700
00:28:12,609 --> 00:28:14,110
Well, look at Tim there,

701
00:28:14,569 --> 00:28:16,446
with the photos
of his ugly children.

702
00:28:17,447 --> 00:28:19,157
Ivan and his flowerpots.

703
00:28:19,574 --> 00:28:21,368
Poor Andrea's still hoping
Destiny's Child

704
00:28:21,576 --> 00:28:22,452
get back together.

705
00:28:22,744 --> 00:28:23,662
Don't you see?

706
00:28:24,454 --> 00:28:26,122
These people still have hope.

707
00:28:28,249 --> 00:28:29,793
- CHLOE: Excuse me.
- Yeah.

708
00:28:30,001 --> 00:28:32,337
- Who's had this
job the longest?
- Um...

709
00:28:32,545 --> 00:28:33,630
maybe me.

710
00:28:34,255 --> 00:28:35,382
I've been at it
two whole months.

711
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:37,300
- Huh.
- Oh. Anyone else?

712
00:28:37,634 --> 00:28:38,259
No.

713
00:28:38,635 --> 00:28:39,928
Other than Leila, of course.

714
00:28:40,136 --> 00:28:42,555
- Leila, your boss?
- Yeah. She started
as a moderator

715
00:28:42,764 --> 00:28:44,057
before the company blew up.

716
00:28:44,724 --> 00:28:46,059
She was the first of us.

717
00:28:46,685 --> 00:28:47,560
Thanks.

718
00:28:48,853 --> 00:28:51,064
Leila knew Nick, she had
access to the videos.

719
00:28:51,272 --> 00:28:52,190
If she's behind this...

720
00:28:52,399 --> 00:28:54,567
She's known what we've been
doing every step of the way.

721
00:28:56,569 --> 00:28:58,780
Dan, I need you to see if
you can trace the videos

722
00:28:58,988 --> 00:29:00,699
