particular now.

723
00:29:01,616 --> 00:29:03,785
(sighs) We're looking
at Leila Simms.

724
00:29:09,124 --> 00:29:11,584
I can't believe we had the
killer right under our nose.

725
00:29:11,960 --> 00:29:13,086
And she's gone.

726
00:29:14,796 --> 00:29:17,632
Touché, Leila. Touché.

727
00:29:26,141 --> 00:29:27,016
Luci?

728
00:29:28,893 --> 00:29:30,103
Luci, you home?

729
00:29:31,187 --> 00:29:33,022
